@@TJvTVCascadeOption
<TITLE TJvTVCascadeOption type>
Summary
  Enumerates different methods how checks are propagated when toggling a checkbox node on or off.
Description
  The TJvTVCascadeOption type is an enumeration used to determine how checks are propagated when
  toggling a checkbox node on or off.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvTVCascadeOption.poOnCheck
Propagate to child nodes only when the node is toggled to the on state.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvTVCascadeOption.poOnUnCheck
Propagate to child nodes only when the node is toggled to the off state.

